In order to complete the sub task "Close the terminal after viewing the successful installation information", we can see the information in the terminal that the installation is completed, so we only need to close the terminal.
The following is a JSON format operation, which is used to click the Close button to close the terminal window:```json
[
    {"action_type": "MouseAction", "mouse_action_type": "click", "mouse_button": "left", "mouse_position": {"width": 833, "height": 152}}
]
```
